data.text:
Royal response from Their Royal Highnesses The Prince of Beira and Infanta Maria Francisca, Duchess of Coimbra on the occasion of their 26th and 25th birthdays respectively.

Born Afonso de Santa Maria Miguel Gabriel Rafael on 25th March 1996 in Lisbon to Duarte Pio and Isabel, The Duke and Duchess of Braganza.

Born Maria Francesca Isabel Micaela Gabriela Rafaela Paula on 3rd March 1997 in Lisbon to Duarte Pio and Isabel, The Duke and Duchess of Braganza.

The reply is in the form of a letter thanking me for my birthday wishes to Their Royal Highnesses and also included is a family photo of the Portuguese Royal Family.
